          <p class='first-para'>
            Given the severity of the problems he describes, does my right hon. Friend agree that it is pitiful that out of the more than 400 Labour MPs, just two are present for the debate?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_208wh' title='Col. 208WH &mdash; HC Deb 09 January 2002 vol 377 c208WH' name='column_208wh' href='#column_208wh' rel='bookmark'>208WH</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0377P0_20020109_WH_16'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-redwood' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
