          <p class='first-para'>
            It is noticeable that there are not many here. Many Labour Members are deeply embarrassed by the state of the railways and do not wish to have to hear again just how bad it is. Perhaps many of them have not been able to get here yet this morning because the trains are so appallingly bad. They are now taking to the inadequate roads.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0377P0_20020109_WH_17'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-julian-brazier' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
